'''Renown''' is a Negotiation [[Key Words|key word]] for [[Smith]].

==Effect==
In game description: "'''Renown''': When destroyed, deal 1 damage to your core argument per stack of '''Renown'''. 

At the end of your turn, this deals 1 damage for every two stacks to a random opponent argument. At the start of your turn, '''Renown''' is reduced by 1 stack.

'''Renown''' is an argument with 3 resolve.".

